1. *Spava* se tokom noći. (He/She is sleeping during the night.)
2. Mi smo *spavali* ceo dan. (We have been sleeping all day.)
3. Ona je *spavala* u krevetu. (She was sleeping in the bed.)
4. Dete je *spavalo* u kolicima. (The child was sleeping in the stroller.)
5. On će *spavati* cijelu noć. (He will be sleeping all night.)
6. *Spavam* u kući. (I am sleeping at home.)
7. Oni će *spavati* do podneva. (They will be sleeping until noon.)
8. Mi smo *spavali* do jutra. (We have been sleeping until morning.)
9. Ona će *spavati* u krevetu. (She will be sleeping in the bed.)
10. Dete je *spavalo* u svojoj sobi. (The child was sleeping in his/her room.)